title: Earth's Kitchen
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, Organic, Western, Beer/Wine, Australian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe attached to Wilsons Organics market. Offers some vegetarian and vegan dishes. Has plant-milk, organic muesli, scrambled tofu, and a vegan breakfast. Salads, pizza, veggie burger, sandwiches, and daily specials at lunch and dinner. A few vegan desserts as well.
